  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Campo Smith Apartments provide excellent accommodation in a picturesque location with lovely mountain views all around. The ski lifts and ski school are beside the apartments and the resort centre is a 15 minute walk or a short bus ride away. The neighbouring Hotel Rivè has an indoor pool and a wellness centre with sauna, massage, Turkish bath and beauty treatments (all payable locally). Facilities include the Mezzaluna restaurant and bar with live music at weekends, ski hire shop, free Wi-Fi throughout and ski storage room.</p>]]></description>
