  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All apartments have kitchenette with fridge, microwave, coffee-maker and toaster, living area with Sky satellite TV and bathroom with shower and wc. Studios have a double and single sofa bed. 2-room apartments are either on one level with double bedroom and double sofa bed and single sofa bed in living area or are split level with double bedroom upstairs with extra bed and living area with double sofa bed downstairs. There are some larger 2-room apartments on one level, sleeping up to 6, with a double bedroom and a double sofa bed and bunk beds in the living area.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
